room.1.longdesc
	You are in a large, tarnished brass bed in an old, musty bedroom.\ncobwebs hang from the ceiling.  A few rays of light filter through\nthe shutters.  There is a nightstand nearby with a single wooden\ndrawer.  The door west creaks in the breeze.  A macabre portrait\nhangs to the left of an empty fireplace.
room.1.shortdesc
	You are in the bedroom.
