	You are at the top of the castle tower.  Far off in\nthe distance you can see a dirt road leading to the\nmoat.  Across the moat is a small village.  A small\npath winds west from the south end of the road.
room.38.shortdesc
	You're at top of tower.
room.39.door
	-1
room.39.exit.e
	30
room.39.longdesc
	You are standing below a small window.  A small\npath winds its way east.
room.39.shortdesc
