room.41.longdesc
	You are in a huge anteroom to an even larger, mysterious\nchamber.  A chilling wind seems to blow at you from all\nsides, and a deathlike, vapid black mist surrounds your\nfeet.  Hundreds of sinister looking bats cling to the\nceiling and eye you with a spine-tingling anticipatory\npleasure.  Two dark, foreboding passages exit to the east\nand west, and a steep sloping corridor descends NW.
room.41.shortdesc
	You're in a huge anteroom.
room.42.door
	-1
room.42.exit.leave
	u
room.42.exit.se
	41
room.42.exit.u
	41
room.42.longdesc
	You're on a steep ledge above a seemingly bottomless pit.\nSkeletal remains still cling to various rocks jutting out\nof the pit.  Horrible, blood-curdling wails can be heard\nfrom deep within the pit, obviously cries from the dead.\nA steep corridor rises to the SE.
room.42.shortdesc
	You're at a steep ledge.
