			@set(value.master,3)
		@endif
	@endif
room.43.exit.leave
	e
room.43.longdesc
	You are in the chamber of the master of the castle,\nCount Vladimir!  Pictures depicting scenes of tranquil\nTransylvanian countrysides line the walls.  A huge\nportrait of Vladimir's brother, Count Dracula, hangs\nupon the near wall.  In the center of the room is a\nlarge, ominous, mahogany coffin.
room.43.shortdesc
	You're in the Master chamber.
