room.77.longdesc
	You are in a room whose walls are covered with graffiti.\nThe messages range from "FRODO LIVES" to filthy remarks\nconcerning the parental lineage of werewolves.  A rocky\npath goes south.  A low tunnel leads east.
room.77.shortdesc
	You are in the graffiti room.
