room.85.longdesc
	This is the disco room.  Multicolored lasers pulsate\nwildly to the beat of badly mixed music.  A stairway\ndown is barely visible through the glare.  A large\npassage exits south, and a smaller one leads west.
room.85.shortdesc
	This is the disco room.
