	85
room.87.exit.w
	86
room.87.longdesc
	You have entered the land of the living dead, a\nlarge, desolate room.  Although it is apparently\nuninhabited, you can hear the awful sounds of\nthousands of lost souls weeping and moaning.\nIn the east corner are stacked the remains of\ndozens of previous adventurers who were less\nfortunate than yourself.  To the north is a\nforeboding passage.  A path goes west.
room.87.shortdesc
	You are in the land of the living dead.
room.88.door
	-1
room.88.exit.leave
	n
room.88.exit.n
	86
room.88.longdesc
	You are in the lair of the cyclops.  The broken bones of\nprevious explorers are strewn about the room.  One huge\ncontact lens lies on a high table.  The cyclops seems\nto be gone.  A splintered door exits north.
room.88.shortdesc
	You are in the cyclops' lair.
room.89.door
	-1
room.89.exit.leave
	w
room.89.exit.w
	90
room.89.longdesc
	You are in an extremely cold chamber imbedded deep\nwithin the glacier.  Stalagtites of ice hang from\nthe ceiling far above you.  An ominous tunnel leaves\nto the west.
room.89.shortdesc
	You are deep inside the glacier.
room.90.door
	-1
room.90.exit.e
	89
room.90.exit.enter
	u
room.90.exit.s
	65
room.90.longdesc
	You are in a long, bending tunnel.  With your lamp\nyou can barely make out exits to the south and east.
room.90.shortdesc
	You are in a cold, bending tunnel.
room.91.afterlook
	@if @carry(12) @and @true(@get(value.wiz)) @then
