room.93.longdesc
	This is the wizard's throne room.  Scattered about\nthe room are various magical items.  A long message\nin ancient runes is carved into the southern wall.  It\ntranslates roughly as "Beware the power of the Wizard,\nfor he is master of this place".  Two green paths go\nsouth and east, and a marble walk leads west.
room.93.shortdesc
	You are in the throne room.
room.94.door
	-1
room.94.exit.e
	93
room.94.exit.leave
	e
room.94.longdesc
	You are in the wizard's cache, a large room whose walls\nare inlaid with jewels.  A majestic marble walk leads to\nthe east.
room.94.shortdesc
	This is the Wizard's cache.
